name: Bohemian Madhubani
description: 'Bohemian Madhubani' Fusion of Pop and Traditional Art. Madhubani is a famous Indian traditional Art form and Freddy Mercury is a famous Pop Icon. Fun fact: I studied in the same town as Freddy (Panchgani, India). Queen as was a fantastic band and Bohemian Rhapsody was a wonderful movie and music track.
